;&lt;/td&gt;&lt;/tr&gt;&lt;/table&gt;&lt;/td&gt;&lt;/tr&gt;&lt;tr&gt;&lt;td style="border-collapse: collapse;"&gt;&lt;table border="0" cellpadding="0" cellspacing="0" style="font-size: 16px; line-height: 24px;" width="100%"&gt;&lt;tr&gt;&lt;td style="border-collapse: collapse; padding: 0px 10px;"&gt;&lt;p style="font-family: Georgia, serif; margin: 16px 0;"&gt;习近平总统的政府在涉及地理经济战略方面表现出了越来越高的迹象。为了避免在全球贸易体系中白宫隔离，北京提出了一些新技巧。&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p style="font-family: Georgia, serif; margin: 16px 0;"&gt;回到唐纳德·特朗普（Donald Trump）的第一个学期结束时，中国与欧盟达成了&lt;a href="https://links.message.bloomberg.com/s/c/IV8bxViYhUKa2E8nWtb3i86HhNgAscAMEZc1EfhAAxWrneUWBX8LFEUHhJx1ArBcApR6a1IYYwylv0O4fuF6cbtKbKUjt8IXOUzy3y2bqWOevXXelyc6UCToeM8LjNlf0hc0ckgovTXlkyCZvs3beQ7mDAvsx8KNoOb3UoI8JqH0fiwAqYEnWcDBimD4vC2gvBiktd08ZjAK60XHTKuGDLG_cfUYWIXjMeEV9wyCSI4c1NHrTMIPH5UpSpIryVk7rGCsWS5ZFryoFFwJiJQqe-mLRWVNVkPOWzX3QL_5SBZd7YNpkw9lEYTcuZrQ7RqCt829yG5YtO7RqoxjfJMpi45fXafCsuqLqMoQnwNVQ9GS8j3eg5sD6qFW2BDD8hpD7wuUZ_Md6160LLDCsH25yd9fHYGezLxTcXEw_cNe28s35Xe3DSSrNaeByFwHbHoK0NxjvCJHkV5YPWKTtvRLKgRCqGiv7t_lpU6QPtuGVZEi7aQGNLwQb7Hz2RNXGvTq3WPwsyl0Yy5fJja_ibize35VcOj4Wa71d1_aeqq0sn1lm_kIMqvjR1ERAP-xa1dUE3AHUEPXnRQwyFbJo6bSLoHQ6jQNH1pbzFsXfqXfBQ/4u1zjt5qNbiywq2tW_dkkktwpTE1Fm18/8" target="_blank"&gt;具有里程碑意义的投资协议&lt;/a&gt;，这似乎是鼓励它的举动（请参阅上周的&lt;a href="https://links.message.bloomberg.com/s/c/OW3Sw46-BNiP_ZFR0WhEeYIbVh0o7lWx1ZoR1DD0EGlSm56azA8Jd_A_pE9co5dcjS9J4MsTjKINwDU67ardHt9WDsZzpfsEQMXBeFqUjJOyRzyOIwDfjRkrBWAeRCDGBuMjTtfjzyUfBjzffH1zCZoQ7gCvibU0X8LRBjEJ9LOBEvaFD9ortHI6SDuUQgoRZjs4uOODq8W8MDe29QwdDhm_hgbwgigjOWDE16e3mjid-QofwOSPccWcpm7ZmwcifHdgtFjt8HPn-cCw4gMmHIBacXr07Ox-rHwEC20DxNwYtMf84JYLPAt_ldyDd7g3rqooBxs-N3AoEUlezFazmvZNPdgGePLL81dyt_HdVUDNVws9dRDUeUtzlg/sf4K6iKSik72GgKbIDsU7Mr723KbYk_b/8" target="_blank"&gt;新闻通讯&lt;/a&gt;）作为中立球员而不是我们的盟友。但是，欧盟在北京批准了几位欧洲立法者以报复该集团对中国对人权关注的制裁之后， &lt;a href="https://links.message.bloomberg.com/s/c/ZqeYjpsGhuKQUL6Bo2trwVzGNUxRwdi6m9PAW4_tbzFaeEx9dirk5dQ1RoiKmQ-yB6Tmt7cUBaGw7MjKtuiKj-zNwXHk_tU5rXzS-fJMNSp7Hjr1g6wrzIdwt6yPiQYBhqMilYL01IdZ1OOKnhIiXCZRzzTCyeUfzCk1K_QoVP5cZdHiCP_zLt2y4TQgtaHCQTa7Y-UmHHy5QfpunkPo5gwXDndct9vednNFPBw16BwMFa39wBVu7tt41bvqpT1HwChBPqx76UMQ89nn6_Vu_li2-hybTiboekliG_laE5lrS1eiFnWwFBozbok_Kjz4vLeTACvJuIkIW-lR4EAbi9DNmJ8PPLkWw43LVdQRlUqtKPJfuDWsKgAS6g/0FNQZ7rufYa8CiHGALdql6dhIB8WVUIV/8" target="_blank"&gt;搁置了批准&lt;/a&gt;。&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p style="font-family: Georgia, serif; margin: 16px 0;"&gt;当时，中国似乎优先考虑战术冲突而不是战略冲突。另一种选择是忽略欧盟&lt;a href="https://links.message.bloomberg.com/s/c/lUtQ95_1h_huSEYKyZpcKMrpmOvTUj_vOFufmfv_NJZKkmSKAUqNrWyLxyGv8F9v8UpKP2qKevOTfvZHUX4dMzSepH4XPBTTXSsY7EkPHf7TC5NQXX5UluYxUAChkcr6DugAo6j5qHP1QTuKYrG-qZ2I2E6oM_6_YZlIM1jqMZaHpnuIUcI_QZIdPirgM_S1ESuzXmMKfszgILkbXIyMRx0ojnrALO9ATWztpbHm2Vl3Suee5weOV10poJadiEgmXw-LsZXpq7EbsstqE86O3tMw2BHLfZzMa8P2ht3Axrj6O5vXBLWkvYfEUAMRVRg96OJIsNM895rClABRFrwCVhFzEosJxJHJ7ddRZwOFexOQahZbTHvpujzc0g/3I52vg9Pt9fw6mHaVAjfYxC4Ek7vv_Xj/8" target="_blank"&gt;有限的制裁&lt;/a&gt;，并继续专注于批准大型经济同意。快进到本周：北京刚刚&lt;a href="https://links.message.bloomberg.com/s/c/iVk_zNH3fowSkKJul5tFcO_mK64qkBpWqzqAEZRivQ-VkyphIok37Py1clRHn1f3mqc9eK5Day8iRdiltJrdtWm7x7td6TCoVlzlyG81QNZSs7HPds7nbJlngpDxCMzUTBPd57NbwKsAy5QcBPSjs2mLmyEaBYjsIaTC8zLBup512mCw7_GNhIJWbbUKy4ZVOKZJ6wnXr5VhF21SEoATa7DeD2DF3uAqG4xm2iWm0FFTKnyE2xx40de9DLvgj5aydvUnx2uYxVaerTmLOlT1Z-eZ6ytrbypwnZEkOKBlMI1eTnr57tmhWHEnjqcCoPcXyE_vdb7j_jmACtWoO7aAu-KYFOoV1NP6vOOI5pWAtQCLcVzj0bd9i9wk53E/EUq9Epe6UmFe7JyXcF0FL0w1ke0AJla2/8" target="_blank"&gt;取消了对那些欧洲立法者的处罚&lt;/a&gt;。窗口可能已经为旧的投资协议而关闭，但是此举为中国寻求对抗美国的合作伙伴时提供了新的外观。&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p style="font-family: Georgia, serif; margin: 16px 0;"&gt;这种新方法 - 如下所述，在上个月关于韩国的举动中也可以明显看出，这对于特朗普的新发现的贸易社会谈判中尉，前进基金经理斯科特·贝森特（Scott Bessent）的工作甚至更加艰巨。财政部长&lt;a href="https://links.message.bloomberg.com/s/c/SA5tVWb3zacEpEUC7ZzlUNpHmsmpJfCsHPnVlsT7Poqdf95fgNeaW-VG9MXpfmz9wOikX__x-eDy4YEQr3XUCuAGoAdveQCV3_yswlj9--qLah7GfJiQ-jDmyYvTBpBfSiQ66jorueND4EjCw0FhH4xWrtk3J5FnqnDsaULu4QJFjbKOCCW_jCKzLW6fImIkNdzPrGF_BUToX-mfvzbjAf15xKlzApgm1g7kSKvCXAwRPl_1A4GiJcMjUK_srCSiNQmGufClbJOEMytOks17vw1rM7qPYfSqDvPqbo_mMsAR-ar7bsq25PVTguEw99Z1IzsNpyErK9AKSIuowrjTLXioAnUl1x-C8cVNwZT_ID0hm_WZxYR8JbxBwpY/r1j4TNgPotltJANJhehEPaP2cnBsXdKu/8" target="_blank"&gt;提出了与美国贸易伙伴达成交易的愿景&lt;/a&gt;，以加大对中国的压力。现在，他和特朗普可能需要考虑北京更加复杂的对手。 &lt;/p&gt;&lt;div class="body-image" style="margin: 20px 0px;"&gt;&lt;!--[if mso]&gt;&lt;table width="550"&gt;&lt;tr&gt;&lt;td&gt;&lt;img alt="" src="https://assets.bwbx.io/images/users/iqjWHBFdfxIU/ic_dU8O43jfw/v0/-1x-1.jpg" width="550"/&gt;&lt;/td&gt;&lt;/tr&gt;&lt;/table&gt; &lt;div style="display:none"&gt;&lt;![endif]--&gt;&lt;img alt="" src="https://assets.bwbx.io/images/users/iqjWHBFdfxIU/ic_dU8O43jfw/v0/-1x-1.jpg" style="display: block; width: 530px; margin: auto;" /&gt;&lt;!--[if mso]&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;![endif]--&gt;&lt;div style="font-size: 14px; line-height: 130%; margin-top: 8px;"&gt;美国财政部长Scott Bessent&lt;i&gt;摄影师：Al Drago/Bloomberg&lt;/i&gt; &lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;table align="center" cellpadding="0" cellspacing="0" width="auto"&gt;&lt;tr&gt;&lt;td align="center" colspan="2" style="padding: 0 0px;" valign="top"&gt; &lt;a href="https://links.message.bloomberg.com/s/c/BmNZoGu0MlWxPjddCu0Tu2WMiTOlPzE_Nvz5GbVOt2B0c9lG2lMiJSjMTqbTkvBeRMZTdvSWIqko1x_qPOLt-cb1yXboxuir5Xv2UbgYeBrWMhWt1UhCLFdQqyRajFfba1wPXR0LgshecPI9AftEB5pRKgARahs8-QvtJg0ug6k1qO3eW7l9rz35zYda-6nmBz26jPYAiFkmhyp44NC6mTsRzMhHHN57Tg82X9MjDKdRREeDKXdtr5KUY9iRIT1Xg3_gz7Mk891ne_wq_W2hRpAlDw1eL18zQ4hCA1-L0tbLmyfKPHDA8uy51tkmPhVcU5AK25-CdDX9WZDULxnEbQlBIqESEo3Ksei3H_DhwKSZYMDiACpZ_9qLwxxldVQYPaG0w0h2Rscsd9Ut5QfPYOo2bKv0aYhx-tESAGZE3qPH3fj7aAow7a8vkci0QpHdavXXRamf48T-hzZ9PWN3xQVtR10hpL2zbnBf_nsqHnOGD7GNVLLzUqbWUaNRddJIXx9D4A-A8ByKqd9pQMUvx2-XNprnKluLUx_o-NBroO36xDzBIZKyWovcsAQyU5ZxS1pAN2WWvkn3X15FczUSQMxOc0m4trm4yl2wDdHa_3I14fg32Z3CXWjzDlSPyW-Be-TAiGFk87UkM0_vBJWoUqu92tUjotGIxcIIRAzojlAIuoHGLZR6riiEILCUUQ/u40xVs1M8t6bmcPahWaWAWmY14Km1LDP/8" target="_blank"&gt;&lt;img alt="" border="0" class="lihide" src="https://sli.bloomberg.com/imp?s=868