/strong&gt; Uber首次推出了针对老年人的&lt;a href="https://links.message.bloomberg.com/s/c/MPScI5klYkXIlI6lck9grPLxWl8XAIw4EsJ8eg8Jvc1WhWiDl04vXGtoNvV8NZEKKPFQbBZLSduA3VJhI3j1zlitQh_6Bwe7pSYoMgO91NsRv2N7JXpVOKbnWcVIs7_UNYy7sk1oKPjuyEPR4Owk4lC9SqELAru6umZASsnO29sLltV7-pmlp_L9n8nJ4IFrj_a1RZ6i3c2PyYp1NRDfINpQMqbaOPPAHwN1-v8V5ZRuL6X3U7oNTpTnx76f62eocK0T4vOQuQkVS4qJSb342FKMPUUnLJe3hBNMpDTY0kjippxAyg2ZvNO23KIhZQsFc3NN9Kf17ensEh1Y_1nodWsJA0XOUij2f9n1XbaV_STBRwSnQRArmrDiqA/NHz3GiJZePs3FQcIAUMvBNKPaHwEaBYq/8" target="_blank" title="链接到故事"&gt;新型流线型乘车应用程序&lt;/a&gt;，希望能获得更大的大型市场。竞争对手Lyft迅速跟随，称其简化的老年人应用程序将在几天内开始使用。&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p style="font-family: Georgia, serif; margin: 16px 0;"&gt;&lt;strong style="font-family: Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif;"&gt;间谍招聘：&lt;/strong&gt;美国中央情报局正在使用埃隆·马斯克（Elon Musk）的X等&lt;a href="https://links.message.bloomberg.com/s/c/6QP2EzpS59ECYYwxaBaYJWZ2lazQRyFPat0_wXTmGdscYgZecbu7zraAbWRdT2BFBU6TocAqV47nqdUmLmJSPQCXXFQshKC8roSV6jGtuI5OzhCePhCBmlRpXUiTCfDqMVKSjSamE7AjNd_ai3ADgxtsd2peJhDY-fvMPJU0l4rJRyzaLy6CH1MQ_WY7OnJj7oI3FsBCloMhzoXF86JG-Qk59tRXc-_6tPj30USI_ttFzK-OenzSDJoRRsE4xR20KHgk43p1eOGA_L19nHVBWNxR0qdFqciCUKFMlIYYQdKysExMKPnlFlDpnC7pdylf-WrhTfwtW3Pdlo63NqAcdPDdyERLnRVcrp65E3gU0cGnensLGJduBAnmKg/A6smTxuoXZjsIujkZsQ-jj0BRH_h_oc4/8" target="_blank" title="链接到故事"&gt;社交媒体网络上的视频&lt;/a&gt;，试图招募中国官员提供有关政府的信息。&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p style="font-family: Georgia, serif; margin: 16px 0;"&gt;&lt;strong style="font-family: Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif;"&gt;哈罗德（Harrods Hack）：&lt;/strong&gt;伦敦豪华百货公司（London Luxury Department Store） &lt;a href="https://links.message.bloomberg.com/s/c/8dpNnQ1lP5xxwFMJcMqH_0L0EyPNF52i_PM4p0Pb0zsLlPJMLgV4r2qenDRg6BSY0ONpdeVuyZppHypiziyRs9V9PjM33sZ_dQNXbljQsMoFytM4-iWAUoXfzaikl03_c4qJ_4j6W0L8FIbh6t9OgHTWzv9akg557nxMPH-9wNicbbKgjYVYs1LCvO6l9GqvYLHjGwDqWYN4_YhHcuzeTHWCZ5i9-06l9i5qD6TuBlAw5XAxZl_iUC1XL4B3hVFIbv6w9LdIrUmrGdPSEz7TAFp4lbVX0ZE8lmx0XtNZFUFuQSCKByBl-PZDPraR3cAcar75j7s4I86wYmOu74ry2B8Yl-RsDnR54KDD3Uk9es-HhvQx8S60_Nygog/aBChOKNGe4lUN8LpNCKEdLlnqG7ofNz2/8